fields.name: Life’s Secret
fields.value: "Look up at the stars and not down at your feet. Try to make sense of what you see, and wonder about what makes the universe exist. Be curious." — Stephen Hawking

fields.name: That’s me
fields.value: "I ain't an educated man as all you Fleet Street preachers know, It's just the simple things in life get my motor running, ready to go. If I can make you smile I will raise my glass, an' if you don't like it then, baby, you can kiss my ass!"
